nodes.text: The Vorkaa system was a star system that was located within the Mid Rim's Graador sector. The system shared its name with the Vorkaan delegation, which met with the New Republic Minister of State Mokka Falanthas in 16 ABY.
The Vorkaa system was established in the StarWars.com Online Companion to the 2009 reference book The Essential Atlas, which placed the system in grid square I-17.
